data.description: 3.125% assumable mortgage in a well established neighborhood! The perfect 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home with upgraded kitchen, baths, and solar panels. The home just had a fresh coat of paint and professional deep clean. This mid-century-style ranch home has been tenderly attended to and tastefully upgraded. Comfortable, large living spaces perfect for entertaining and a large covered porch. This oversized lot in highly desirable Candleridge has mature trees, is close to walking trails and parks. Seller's Solar Panels are assumable to lower your electric payments to $200 a month. Property features hand scraped wood floors, whole home re-insulation, soft close kitchen drawers and cabinets, and custom drapes and window treatments. Call listing agent for more info on assumable mortgage. Fridge, furniture, washer and dryer, TV negotiable in purchase.
